In [542]:
#years = [2017,2018,2019,2020]

years = range(1975,2021)

base = 'https://www.basketball-reference.com/leagues/NBA_{}_per_poss.html'


nba_per = []


for year in years:
    
    
    pp_url = base.format(year)
    

    #print(pp_url)
    
    nba_test = pd.DataFrame()
    
    source = requests.get(pp_url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(source.content,'lxml')
    header = [th.getText() for th in soup.findAll('tr',limit=2)[0].findAll('th')]
    header = header[1:]
    rows = soup.findAll('tr')[1:]
    players = [[td.getText() for td in rows [i].findAll('td')] for i in range (len(rows))]
    
    #nba_per.append(players)
    
    current = pd.DataFrame(players,columns=header)
    current['year'] = year
    nba_per.append(current)
    
    

    #nba_test.append(current,ignore_index=True)


#current = pd.DataFrame(nba_per,columns=header)


#nba_per

GETTING MISSING YEARS
In [869]:
years = range(2018,2021)

advbase = 'https://www.basketball-reference.com/leagues/NBA_{}_advanced.html'


nba_ad = []


for year in years:
    
    
    adv_url = advbase.format(year)
    

    #print(pp_url)
    
    source = requests.get(adv_url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(source.content,'lxml')
    header = [th.getText() for th in soup.findAll('tr',limit=2)[0].findAll('th')]
    header = header[1:]
    rows = soup.findAll('tr')[1:]
    players = [[td.getText() for td in rows [i].findAll('td')] for i in range (len(rows))]
    
    #nba_per.append(players)
    
    current = pd.DataFrame(players,columns=header)
    current['year'] = year
    nba_ad.append(current)
In [899]:
nba_adv = pd.concat(nba_ad, ignore_index=True)
